{"tid":611353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[報應] 蝗童對住𨋢掣痾尿搞到短路，墮𨋢槽重傷","createTime":"2018-03-31T02:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T09:57:25.000Z","uid":34701,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9a1179a0028d353c8b1c8f71b5ebbb962d452533","tid":611353,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"內地的小童似乎對電梯特別情有獨鍾，不時都出現各式各樣小童破壞電梯的新聞，而且很多都要付出沉重代價。浙江義烏一名6歲小童，對着電梯的按鈕板撒尿，引發短路，使電梯停頓、電梯門打開，他踏出電梯後，從7樓墮下，昏迷16日。<br />\n<br />\n這名大命的小童，去年8月3日在浙江義烏一個商場獨自乘坐電梯，他見周圍沒人，竟然脫褲向着按鈕鍵撒尿，這時電梯短路，電梯停頓，門突然打開，男童便從門中走出，從高處掉下，男童被人發現時，已經陷入休克，身體多處受傷，即時送院搶救，醫生檢查後發現他顱腦損傷、肺部裂傷、多處骨折，留院16日才醒過來。<br />\n<br />\n重慶一名小童，同樣在獨自乘坐電梯之時，向着按鈕板射尿，這次電梯到達他要去的樓層時，門只開微開便立即關上，燈光全熄，按鈕不斷閃爍，嚇得他不顧是否乾淨，猛按開門鍵，緊張得跳來跳去。<br />\n<br />\n這名重慶小童的家長否認是兒子破壞電梯，更辯稱他「尿不到這麼高」，引發數以萬計網民怒批，更令公安部特別發文，要求家長好好管教小童。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180330/large/1522418659_cced.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180330%2Flarge%2F1522418659_cced.jpg&h=8478c802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180330/large/1522418660_fff9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180330%2Flarge%2F1522418660_fff9.jpg&h=1f5c5ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180331/58016191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58016191&d=ab76clmwX5BnS3AadcFD1CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d7233f6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58016191&h=28012b9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180331/58016191</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e39e67d34cb7c77c55e461b15709bb4fe64464","tid":611353,"uid":52946,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:29:15.000Z","msg":"蝗國是文化道德之國 不容你們港仔就三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efae3024923c603419484dae846468eb85fb788","tid":611353,"uid":39601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebe584e6e9eb4b87d8b0c169718a5efafa7dff3","tid":611353,"uid":34701,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"77e39e67d34cb7c77c55e461b15709bb4fe64464","tid":611353,"uid":52946,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:29:15.000Z","msg":"蝗國是文化道德之國 不容你們港仔就三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"應該將周街痾屎痾尿呢樣傳統習俗列入非物質文化遺產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0f76bede711cef74c0893dbc65868ffad3166a","tid":611353,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"好撚耐啦，條友奇蹟醫返好"},{"pid":"f6946c7d41f0389497bea70bf1e7cf49329fab5f","tid":611353,"uid":86418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"佢既行為唔配戴紅領巾"},{"pid":"59050c3451d59c194070b76dd6b42cd8fd4b27d2","tid":611353,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:44:15.000Z","msg":"咁做有乜目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8980092a8b602debea16ca6612e51324561e49a","tid":611353,"uid":34701,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"59050c3451d59c194070b76dd6b42cd8fd4b27d2","tid":611353,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit